      "end_time": 383501.0,
      "text": "no water molecules, 10 water molecules,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 383501.0,
      "end_time": 385666.0,
      "text": "discrete amounts of these water molecules,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 385666.0,
      "end_time": 387733.0,
      "text": "but there&#39;s so many of them and they&#39;re so small,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 387733.0,
      "end_time": 391500.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s hard to tell that it&#39;s not just completely continuous."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 391500.0,
      "end_time": 393500.0,
      "text": "The same is happening with this light."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 393500.0,
      "end_time": 395233.0,
      "text": "This energy&#39;s extremely small."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 395233.0,
      "end_time": 398166.0,
      "text": "Each violet photon has an extremely small amount of energy"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 398166.0,
      "end_time": 399966.0,
      "text": "that it contributes."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 399966.0,
      "end_time": 402433.0,
      "text": "In fact, if you wanted to know how small it is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 402433.0,
      "end_time": 406007.0,
      "text": "a baseball, a professional baseball player,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 406007.0,
      "end_time": 407633.0,
      "text": "throwing a ball fast, you know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 407633.0,
      "end_time": 410267.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s about 100 joules of energy."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 410267.0,
      "end_time": 413100.0,
      "text": "If you wanted to know how many of these photons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 413100.0,
      "end_time": 415300.0,
      "text": "how many of these violet photons would it take"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 415300.0,
      "end_time": 418323.0,
      "text": "to equal the energy of one baseball"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 418323.0,
      "end_time": 420500.0,
      "text": "thrown at major league speed?"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 420500.0,
      "end_time": 428020.0,
      "text": "It would take about two million trillion"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 428020.0,
      "end_time": 431886.0,
      "text": "of these photons to equal the energy"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 431886.0,
      "end_time": 433800.0,
      "text": "in a baseball that&#39;s thrown."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 433800.0,
      "end_time": 437433.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s why we don&#39;t see this on a macroscopic scale."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 437433.0,
      "end_time": 440766.0,
      "text": "For all intents and purposes, for all we care,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 440766.0,
      "end_time": 444600.0,
      "text": "at a macroscopic level, light&#39;s basically continuous."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 444600.0,
      "end_time": 447434.0,
      "text": "It can deposit any energy whatsoever,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 447434.0,
      "end_time": 449166.0,
      "text": "because the scale&#39;s so small here."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 449166.0,
      "end_time": 450767.0,
      "text": "But if you look at it up close,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 450767.0,
      "end_time": 453533.0,
      "text": "light can only deposit discrete amounts."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 453533.0,
      "end_time": 456500.0,
      "text": "Now, I don&#39;t mean that light can only deposit"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 456500.0,
      "end_time": 458466.0,
      "text": "small amounts."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 458466.0,
      "end_time": 460940.0,
      "text": "Light can deposit an enormous amount of energy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 460940.0,
      "end_time": 462667.0,
      "text": "but it does so in chunks."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 462667.0,
      "end_time": 463766.0,
      "text": "So think about it this way ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 463766.0,
      "end_time": 465700.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s get rid of all this."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 465700.0,
      "end_time": 466866.0,
      "text": "Think about it this way:"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 466866.0,
      "end_time": 471100.0,
      "text": "let&#39;s say you had a detector that&#39;s going to register"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 471100.0,
      "end_time": 472900.0,
      "text": "how much energy it&#39;s absorbing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 472900.0,
      "end_time": 474267.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;ll graph it."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 474267.0,
      "end_time": 477000.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ll graph what this detector&#39;s going to measure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 477000.0,
      "end_time": 480400.0,
      "text": "the amount of energy per time that it measures."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 480400.0,
      "end_time": 484001.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;ll get the amount of energy per time."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 484001.0,
      "end_time": 487633.0,
      "text": "Now, you can absorb huge amounts of energy."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 487633.0,
      "end_time": 490402.0,
      "text": "And on the detector, on a macroscopic scale,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 490402.0,
      "end_time": 491743.0,
      "text": "it just might look like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 491743.0,
      "end_time": 493433.0,
      "text": "You know, you&#39;re getting more and more light energy."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 493433.0,
      "end_time": 495467.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re absorbing more and more energy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 495467.0,
      "end_time": 497100.0,
      "text": "collecting more and more energy."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 497100.0,
      "end_time": 500466.0,
      "text": "But what I&#39;m saying is that, microscopically,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 500466.0,
      "end_time": 501640.0,
      "text": "if you look at this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 501640.0,
      "end_time": 505642.0,
      "text": "what&#39;s happening is, you&#39;ve absorbed one photon here."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 505642.0,
      "end_time": 506600.0,
      "text": "You absorbed another one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 506600.0,
      "end_time": 507700.0,
      "text": "absorbed another one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 507700.0,
      "end_time": 508667.0,
      "text": "absorbed a bunch of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 508667.0,
      "end_time": 510533.0,
      "text": "You keep absorbing a bunch of these photons."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 510533.0,
      "end_time": 513943.0,
      "text": "You can build up a bunch of energy."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 513943.0,
      "end_time": 514766.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s fine."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 514765.99999999994,
      "end_time": 516933.99999999994,
      "text": "It&#39;s just if you looked at it close enough,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 516933.99999999994,
      "end_time": 519632.99999999994,
      "text": "you have this step pattern"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 519633.00000000006,
      "end_time": 522466.00000000006,
      "text": "that&#39;s absorbing photons at a time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 522466.0,
      "end_time": 523733.0,
      "text": "certain numbers of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 523732.99999999994,
      "end_time": 525833.0,
      "text": "Maybe it absorbs three at one moment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 525833.0,
      "end_time": 527234.0,
      "text": "four at another moment."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 527234.0,
      "end_time": 529833.0,
      "text": "But you can&#39;t absorb anything in between."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 529833.0,
      "end_time": 532500.0,
      "text": "It can&#39;t be completely continuous."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 532500.0,
      "end_time": 537133.0,
      "text": "It has to be a discrete all-or-nothing moment"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 537133.0,
      "end_time": 540970.0,
      "text": "of absorption of energy that, on a macroscopic scale,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 540970.0,
      "end_time": 544866.0,
      "text": "looks smooth but on a microscopic scale is highlighted"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 544866.0,
      "end_time": 549066.0,
      "text": "by the fact that light energy is coming in discrete chunks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 549066.0,
      "end_time": 552034.0,
      "text": "described by this equation"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 552034.0,
      "end_time": 562034.0,
      "text": "that gives you the energy of individual photons of light."
    }
  ]
}